msgid ""
"A heavily classified document containing schematics for Northrups ATSV "
"combat walker."
msgstr ""

#: .\walker_item.json
msgid "broken chickenbot"
msgid_plural "broken chickenbots"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'broken chickenbot'}
#: .\walker_item.json
msgid ""
"A broken chicken walker.  Still looks intimidating despite being permanently"
" inoperative, possibly due to the sheer size and mass.  Could be gutted for "
"parts."
msgstr ""

#: .\walker_item.json
msgid "inactive chicken walker"
msgid_plural "inactive chicken walkers"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'inactive chicken walker'}.
#: .\walker_item.json
msgid "The chicken bot rolls out and begins acquiring targets."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'inactive chicken walker'}.
#: .\walker_item.json
msgid ""
"The chicken bot swivels its turret and aims directly at you.  Don your brown"
" pants!"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inactive chicken walker'}
#: .\walker_item.json
msgid ""
"This is an inactive chicken walker.  Using this item involves placing it on "
"the ground, loading the unit with the factory-loaded 5.56 rounds and 40mm "
"cartridge grenades in your inventory (if you wish to divide your ammunition,"
" set aside whatever ammunition you do NOT want to give the robot) and "
"turning it on.  If reprogrammed and rewired successfully the tank drone will"
" then identify you as a friendly, roam around or follow you, and attack all "
"enemies with a built-in firearm and grenade launcher."
msgstr ""

#: .\walker_item.json
msgid "Pathfinder chassis"
msgid_plural "Pathfinder chassis"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': 'Pathfinder chassis'}
#: .\walker_item.json
msgid ""
"What's left when you remove all moving parts and electronics.  It's the "
"skeleton and armor of the pathfinder."
msgstr ""

#: .\walker_item.json
msgid "walker chassis"
msgid_plural "walker chassiss"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'walker chassis'}
#: .\walker_item.json
msgid ""
"An ATSV chassis, hand-forged from scrap.  An integral component for bootleg "
"walkers."
msgstr ""

#: .\walker_item.json
msgid "super chassis"
msgid_plural "super chassiss"
msgstr[0] ""
msgstr[1] ""

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'super chassis'}
#: .\walker_item.json
msgid ""
"An ATSV chassis, carefully crafted with the best materials and to the "
"highest standards possible in a post-Cataclysm world."
msgstr ""

